<https://w3id.org/italia/labour-social-policies/data/social/distribution/MLPSSOCIAL-N-TRIPLES> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Questa \u00E8 la distribuzione N-TRIPLES dell'ontologia del Ministero Del Lavoro e delle Politiche Sociali relativa al dominio GePi definisce in modo strutturato e interoperabile dati, relazioni e concetti relativi alla gestione dei Patti per l\u2019Inclusione Sociale, garantendo uniformit\u00E0 semantica, integrazione informativa e supporto ai processi digitali della piattaforma che \u00E8 parte integrante del Sistema informativo per l'inclusione sociale e lavorativa (SIISL)"@it .
<https://w3id.org/italia/labour-social-policies/data/social/distribution/MLPSSOCIAL-N-TRIPLES> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "This is the distribution in N-TRIPLES of the Labour and Social Policies Ministry Ontology related to the GePi domain defines in a structured and interoperable way the data, relationships, and concepts concerning the management of Social Inclusion Pacts, ensuring semantic uniformity, information integration, and support for the digital processes of the platform, which is an integral part of the Social and Labour Inclusion Information System (SIISL)"@en .
<https://w3id.org/italia/labour-social-policies/data/social/distribution/MLPSSOCIAL-N-TRIPLES> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/format> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/file-type/RDF_N_TRIPLES> .
<https://w3id.org/italia/labour-social-policies/data/social/distribution/MLPSSOCIAL-N-TRIPLES> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/license> <http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/> .
